data.description: PRICE REDUCED $25k!!!Located on an oversized cul de sac lot with sweeping panoramic views of the lake this 5br 3.5 bath pool home is perfect for a large family.  Huge master suite with tray ceilings, 4 windows, and his/hers walk in closets plus a luxurious master bath with dual sinks, roman tub, and separate shower.  Adjoining bedroom could be used for a nursery, office or a gym.  All bedrooms are  oversized and br 2 has its own private bathroom.  Spacious layout with a great room plus a large family room.  Eat in kitchen features ss appliances, granite counters, and breakfast bar and wine cooler.  Sliders lead to a huge screened in pool area on the best lot in the community. Mariner Village is a private gated community that is close to beaches and restaurants in Jupiter, and offers a community pool and other amenities with low HOA fees.
